Class FeatureOneTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dr.nlp.sl.task.FeatureOneTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class FeatureOneTask
extends java.lang.Object
implements Task<java.lang.Void>
    Feature one represents the following feature request: 1. Write a program that identifies sentence boundaries and tokenizes the text in the file "nlp_data.txt" into words. It should correctly process all symbols, including punctuation and whitespace. Every word must fall into a sentence. Create data structures that efficiently express the data you have processed. When your program runs it should output an XML representation of your Java object model.
    Author:
    Stan Livshin
